  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "⚡ NO EXPERIENCE? NO PROBLEM!",
  "description": "<p>Ready to kickstart your career in Sales & Marketing with a team that values energy, growth, and people?<br />If you’ve just finished school, recently ORD-ed, or looking to explore a new path — this is your chance to learn, earn, and travel while building real-world business skills.</p><p>No degree? No experience? No problem. We’ve got the training, mentorship, and opportunities to help you level up fast. 🚀</p><p>🌟 What You’ll Do</p><ul><li>💬 Engage customers face-to-face and represent exciting, trusted brands</li><li>🎯 Drive sales through confident pitching, presentations, and promotions</li><li>🌍 Join local & overseas campaigns — grow your exposure beyond the desk</li><li>🧠 Learn real marketing strategies from mentors who’ve done it before</li><li>🤝 Connect with people and build relationships that open new doors</li></ul><p>💥 What You’ll Get</p><ul><li>Earning potential: $3,000–$6,000/month</li><li>Travel opportunities: Join regional campaigns & overseas trips</li><li>Career progression: Step up as you grow (no seniority limits!)</li><li>Full training provided: We’ll teach you everything you need to succeed</li><li>Vibrant team culture: Work hard, play harder — energy is everything</li><li>Recognition & rewards: Be celebrated for your effort and results</li></ul><p>⚡ You’re Perfect If You’re</p><ul><li>Youthful, confident, and people-oriented</li><li>A fresh grad or recently ORD-ed</li><li>Curious, motivated, and eager to step out of your comfort zone</li><li>Ready to take on challenges and grow fast</li></ul><p>📍 Location: Singapore<br />📩 Apply now and take the first step toward a fun, rewarding career in Sales & Marketing.</p><p>“Opportunities don’t just happen — you create them.”</p>",
